Package com.example.anna.colorgame

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    AsyncResponse
    Interface class that listens to when onPostExecute is called for an AsyncTask.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AlertDialogClass
    This class is used to easily create different alert-dialogs with custom title, message text and buttons, and to show it in specified activity
    ChooseGame
    This class is ChooseGame activity window only available to User with ID 0.
    ConnectToServer
    This class extends AsyncTask and is used to send a request with data to server, and to get a response with data from server.
    DeathmatchGame
    This class is an game activity for Death match game that shows GUI specified for this game.
    DuelGame
    This class is an game activity for Duel game that shows GUI specified for this game.
    Game
    This class is a super class for every game in this application.
    GameOver
    This class is used when the game is over to show AlertDialogs to player.
    HighScore
    This class is an activity that shows high score to user.
    MainFrame
    This class is an activity that is a Login window for the application.
    MainMenu
    This class is MainMenu activity of the application.
    Player
    This class stores data of an Player object.
    PuzzleGame
    This class is an game activity for Puzzle game that shows GUI specified for this game.
    ReceiveDataThread
    This class is a thread that is used in different activities to receive data from server when needed.
    SuperActivity
    This class is a super class for MainFrame, MainMenu, ChooseGame and HighScore activities.
    TrafficGame
    This class is an game activity for Traffic game that shows GUI specified for this game.
